Module 20:  Geomechanics

Learning objectives

After completing this module, you will know how to:

·      Work with task frame

·      Create a task from geomechanics section

·      Work with every single task

20.1.     Task frame

All tasks in the Geomechanics section follow a Task frame including inputs, parameters, output and validation message. The validation message appears if inputs have abnormal data.

Besides, i2G supports plots view including histogram, cross-plot, and log-plot.

Validation

Depend on the marker’s requirements of the equation, i2G will check data input and then show a message if the data is not valid.

Plot Preview

      Depend on the task you calculate, i2G supports histograms and cross-plots preview. You can adjust the parameter on the plot preview, the parameter will be updated on parameter form.

Log-plot Result
